te 优先读取\\\\n+  - `verification_report.md`（V3.6 兼容报告）— 向后兼容\\\\n+- **原子写入**：先写入临时文件（`.verification_report.json.tmp`），完成后 rename 为最终文件名，确保调用方只会看到 `\\\\\\\"completed\\\\\\\"` 或文件不存在两种状态\\\\n+- **Type 字段处理**：typed 命令的记录包含 `type` 字段（值为对应的 VerificationType）；旧格式命令的记录省略 `type` 字段\\\\n+- **manual_verification_checks 不执行**：该字段中的条目不被 sf-verifier 执行，不出现在报告中\\\\n+\\\\n+### 15.4 verification_report.json Schema\\\\n+\\\\n+sf-verifier 产出的结构化验证报告满足以下最小 Schema：\\\\n+\\\\n+```json\\\\n+{\\\\n+  \\\\\\\"schema_version\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"1.0\\\\\\\",\\\\n+  \\\\\\\"work_item_id\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"WI-001\\\\\\\",\\\\n+  \\\\\\\"status\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"completed\\\\\\\",\\\\n+  \\\\\\\"commands\\\\\\\":\\\",\\n  \\\"stderr\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n  \\\"durationMs\\\": 357,\\n  \\\"command\\\": \\\"$OutputEncoding = [System.Text.Encoding]::UTF8; [Console]::OutputEncoding = [System.Text.Encoding]::UTF8; [Console]::InputEncoding = [System.Text.Encoding]::UTF8; git -C \\\\\\\"D:\\\\\\\\code\\\\\\\\temp\\\\\\\\SpecForge\\\\\\\" diff 2c9bec4..e8d8dc2 -- AGENTS.md\\\",\\n  \\\"cwd\\\": \\\"D:\\\\\\\\code\\\\\\\\temp\\\\\\\\SpecForge\\\",\\n  \\\"shell\\\": \\\"pwsh\\\",\\n  \\\"rejected\\\": false,\\n  \\\"timeout\\\": false,\\n  \\\"truncated\\\": {\\n    \\\"stdout\\\": true,\\n    \\\"stderr\\\": false\\n  }\\n}\",\"metadata\":{\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"\",\"time\":{\"start\":1780135000341,\"end\":1780135000715}},\"id\":\"prt_e78507910001MD27dSEXBqVVEt\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_187b21350ffehK5vkTbDHL1ebL\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e78505fca001uXCjvxQwTKCQP7\"},{\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"d216370ad68809ea563c180c8a1ff0df9053c8dd\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":19205,\"input\":1107,\"output\":231,\"reasoning\":75,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":17792}},\"cost\":0,\"id\":\"prt_e78507bb9001w5QzxSDym7xxAr\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_187b21350ffehK5vkTbDHL1ebL\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e78505fca001uXCjvxQwTKCQP7\"}]},{\"info\":{\"parentID\":\"msg_e78505faa001caSqsFKg6q2TBb\",\"role\":\"assi