ecs = \"specs\";\n    // ...\n    \n    // Path construction\n    public static string ResolveProjectPath(string projectRoot, string key, params string[] subpath)\n    {\n        // But wait, you can't do keyof typeof like in TS\n        // So you need to use the const fields directly\n    }\n}\n```\n\nHmm, C# can't do `keyof typeof LAYOUT` to create a union type that enforces valid keys at compile time. The closest would be:\n1. An enum for the keys\n2. A dictionary/switch that maps enum to path\n3. Or just use the const fields directly\n\nActually, the most idiomatic C# approach would be:\n- A static class with const string fields\n- A Roslyn analyzer to catch hardcoded paths (like the lint script)\n- Path.Combine for construction\n\nFor the mapping table, I need to be honest about what C# can and can't do compared to TS:\n\n| 能力 | TypeScript | C# |\n|------|-----------|-----|\n| 门 A 编译期拦截 | ✅ as const 联合类型 | ⚠️ 需 Roslyn Analyzer |\n| 门 B CI lint | ✅ 扫描 .ts | ✅ 扫描 .cs |\n| 门 C 一致性 | ✅ | ✅ |\n| 路径构造函数 | ✅ | ✅ |\n\nLet me write a comprehensive answer about how to adapt this for C#.","time":{"start":1780174412784,"end":1780174429569},"id":"prt_e7aa9dbf0001LSRv3AF4AVrLlt","sessionID":"ses_187b21350ffehK5vkTbDHL1ebL","messageID":"msg_e7aa9cd63001lKLV9GrLr6GMOa"},{"type":"text","text":"我先把 C# 能做到和做不到的拆清楚，再给具体实现。\n\n---\n\n## C# vs TypeScript 能力对比\n\n```\n门 A：编译期拦截路径拼写错误\n  TypeScript:  ✅ as const 联合类型（传错 key 编译报错）\n  C#:          ⚠️ const string 本身不防拼写错误\n               → 需要 Roslyn Analyzer（自定义编译期诊断器）\n\n门 B：CI lint 拦截裸字符串\n  TypeScript:  ✅ 扫描 .ts 文件\n  C#:          ✅ 扫描 .cs 文件（规则不同）\n\n门 C：生成器一致性检查\n  TypeScript:  ✅ bun import .ts\n  C#:          ✅ dotnet tool / 独立脚本读源码或读 JSON\n\n路径构造函数\n  TypeScript:  ✅ resolveProjectPath(root, key)\n  C#:          ✅ Path.Combine + 静态方法\n```\n\n**结论**：C# 没有门 A 的零成本方案，需要写 Roslyn Analyzer 或者放弃门 A 靠门 B/C 兜底。\n\n---\n\n## 两种策略\n\n### 策略一：完全对标 TS（三道门全有）\n\n写一个 Roslyn Analyzer 拦截硬编码路径字符串，成本高，但编译期就能拦。\n\n### 策略二：务实方案（两道门 + 人工 code review）\n\n不写 Analyzer，只靠门 B（lint）+ 门 C（一致性）。C# 项目里大多数路径引用在构建脚本和配置里，手写 `.cs` 里路径的场景比 TS 少。成本极低。\n\n---\n\n## 策略二的具体实现\n\n### 映射表（R7.4 要加的行）\n\n```\n| C#    | `src/Layout/DirectoryLayout.cs`（static class + const string）\n        | 静态方法 + CI lint 拦截裸字符串\n        | render 脚本（读源码或 JSON schema）+ marker 注入\n```\n\n### DirectoryLayout.cs（单一真相源）\n\n```csharp\nnamespace SpecForge.Layout;\n\n/// <summary>\n/// .specforge/ 目录布局的单一真相源。\n/// 所有路径常量定义在此文件，代码中禁止硬编码路径字符串。\n/// </summary>\npublic static class DirectoryLayout\n{\n    /// <summary>项目根下 SpecForge 目录名</summary>\n    public const string SpecDirName = \".specforge\";\n\n    // ---- committed 区 ----\n\n    /// <summary>Project manifest</summary>\n    public const string Manifest = \"manifest.json\";\n\n    /// <summary>项目配置目录</summary>\n    public const string Config = \"config\";\n\n    /// <summary>Work Item 规格目录</summary>\n    public const string Specs = \"specs\";\n\n    /// <summary>Knowledge Graph 数据</summary>\n    public const string KnowledgeGraph = \"knowledge/graph.json\";\n\n    // ---- gitignored 区 ----\n\n    /// <summary>运行时状态目录</summary>\n    public const string Runtime = \"runtime\";\n\n    /// <summary>持久化状态</summary>\n    public const string RuntimeState = \"runtime/state.json\";\n\n    /// <summary>日志目录</summary>\n    public const string Logs = \"logs\";\n\n    /// <summary>Agent Run 归档目录</summary>\n    public const string ArchiveAgentRuns = \"archive/agent_runs\";\n\n    /// <summary>会话归档目录</summary>\n    public const string Sessions = \"sessions\";\n\n    // ---- 路径构造函数 ----\n\n    public static string ResolveProjectPath(string projectRoot, string relativePath)\n    {\n        return Path.Combine(projectRoot, SpecDirName, relativePath);\n    }\n\n    public static string ResolveProjectPath(string projectRoot, string relativePath, params string[] subpath)\n    {\n        var segments = new[] { projectRoot, SpecDirName, relativePath }\n            .Concat(subpath);\n        return Path.Combine(segments.ToArray());\n    }\n\n    public static string SpecPath(string projectRoot, string workItemId, string file)\n    {\n        return Path.Combine(projectRoot, SpecDirName, Specs, workItemId, file);\n    }\n\n    public static string AgentRunArchivePath(string projectRoot, string workItemId, string agentType, int runIndex)\n    {\n        var dirName = $\"{workItemId}-{agentType}-{runIndex}\";\n        return Path.Combine(projectRoot, SpecDirName, ArchiveAgentRuns, dirName);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### CI lint 脚本（扫 .cs 文件）\n\n和 TS 版思路一样，检测规则改为 C# 语法：\n\n```python\n# check-hardcoded-paths.py（伪代码示意）\n# 检测 .cs 文件中的违规模式\n\nVIOLATION_PATTERNS = [\n    r'\".\\.specforge[/\\\\]',      # \".specforge/\"\n    r'\"specforge[/\\\\]',          # \"specforge/\"\n]\n\nSKIP_PATTERNS = [\n    r'^\\s*//',                   # 行注释\n    r'^\\s*\\*',                   # 块注释\n    r'SpecDirName',              # 常量引用\n    r'DirectoryLayout\\.',        # 类引用\n]\n```\n\n### project-rules.md 模板（C# 版）\n\n```markdown\n## 目录布局管理规则\n\n### 单一真相源\n所有 .specforge/ 下的路径定义在 `src/Layout/DirectoryLayout.cs`。\n该文件是路径常量的唯一权威来源。\n\n### 代码中的路径访问\n- ✅ 必须使用 `DirectoryLayout.ResolveProjectPath()` / `.SpecPath()` / `.AgentRunArchivePath()`\n- ❌ 禁止硬编码路径字符串（如 `\".specforge/runtime/state.json\"`、`\"specforge/specs\"`）\n- 新增路径：先在 DirectoryLayout.cs 加 const 字段 + XML 注释，再运行生成脚本\n\n### 自动生成文档（禁止手动编辑）\n（同 TS 版，marker 机制不变）\n\n### CI 检查\n- `lint-hardcoded-paths` job：扫描 .cs 文件中的违规路径字符串\n- `render-layout-consistency` job：运行生成脚本后 git diff 检查一致性\n```\n\n---\n\n## 回到你的问题：R7.4 和映射表怎么改\n\n映射表加一行就够了：\n\n```\n| 技术栈 | 集中定义文件 | 路径访问方式 | 文档生成 |\n|--------|-------------|-------------|---------|\n| TypeScript | directory-layout.ts（as const） | 导出函数 + CI lint | render 脚本 + marker |\n| Python    | layout.py（常量模块）       | 模块常量 + CI lint | 同上 |\n| Go        | layout/constants.go         | 包级常量 + CI lint | 同上 |\n| C#        | Layout/DirectoryLayout.cs    | 静态方法 + CI lint | 同上 |\n| 其他      | directory-layout.json        | 从 JSON 生成代码   | 从 JSON 生成文档 |\n```\n\nA